OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Cburglary and corruption
OL,6,FA former South Wales Police officer
OL,7,Fhas been sent to prison after
OL,8,Fadmitting offences including burglary
OL,9,Fand police corruption.
OL,11,FFollowing an investigation, evidence
OL,12,Flinking ex-Sergeant Ben Cooke to a
OL,13,FBridgend burglary was uncovered.
OL,15,FFurther probing revealed he had also
OL,16,Fcommitted an attempted burglary,
OL,17,Fstolen the front door key from a house
OL,18,Fand misused police computer systems.
