OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Cburglary and corruption
OL,6,FAppearing at Cardiff Crown Court, the
OL,7,F34-year-old pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fburglary, attempted burglary, theft,
OL,9,Fmisuse of police computer systems and
OL,10,Fa police corruption charge.
OL,12,FThe former police officer was
OL,13,Fsentenced to six years and four months.
OL,15,FThe court heard how Cooke had abused
OL,16,Fhis position as an officer by
OL,17,Fpretending to be in possession of a
OL,18,Fsearch warrant to enter a house and
OL,19,Fsteal a safe containing thousands of
OL,20,Fpounds in cash.
