OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Cburglary and corruption
OL,6,FHe had researched his target by
OL,7,Faccessing the police computer and
OL,8,Flooking at intelligence reports.
OL,10,FThe court heard it is thought the safe
OL,11,Fcontained around #16,000 in cash
OL,12,Fthough neither it, nor its contents,
OL,13,Fhave ever been found.
OL,15,FThe prosecutor said Cooke called South
OL,16,FWales Police's anti-corruption unit on
OL,17,FFebruary 9 admitting to doing
OL,18,Fsomething "stupid", but wanted to hand
OL,19,Fhimself in.
