OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Cburglary and corruption
OL,6,FSpeaking after the sentencing the
OL,7,Fchief constable of South Wales Police,
OL,8,FJeremy Vaughan, expressed how the
OL,9,Fformer police officer had not only let
OL,10,Fhimself down, but also, the wider
OL,11,Fpolice service. He also stated that
OL,12,FCooke's "wholly unacceptable
OL,13,Fbehaviour" had "destroyed any trust
OL,14,Fthe communities of South Wales had in
OL,15,Fhim as a police officer."
