OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Cburglary and corruption
OL,6,FHe added: "The vast majority of the
OL,7,F6,000-plus officers and staff who work
OL,8,Ffor South Wales Police conduct
OL,9,Fthemselves impeccably and work
OL,10,Ftirelessly to protect the public,
OL,11,Fthose very few who choose to breach
OL,12,Fthe standards expected of them
OL,13,Fundermine the public's trust in
OL,14,Fpolicing.
OL,16,F"There is no room for this type of
OL,17,Fconduct in South Wales Police."
