OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Cburglary and corruption
OL,6,FJudge Tracey Lloyd-Clarke said Cooke
OL,7,Fhad thrown away his good character and
OL,8,F10 years of exemplary service in the
OL,9,Fforce, tarnishing the reputation of
OL,10,FSouth Wales Police and of policing
OL,11,Fgenerally.
OL,13,FRosamund Rutter, for Cooke, said the
OL,14,Ffather-of-two was ashamed of his
OL,15,Fbehaviour and realised he had let his
OL,16,Ffamily down, let his former colleagues
OL,17,Fdown, let South Wales police down, and
OL,18,Fbrought the police service into
OL,19,Fdisrepute.
