OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Cburglary and corruption
OL,6,FShe said the defendant had spent 10
OL,7,Fyears of his life "upholding the law
OL,8,Fand protecting people", and what he
OL,9,Fdid in January and February this year
OL,10,Fwas "inexplicable".
OL,12,FShe said references before the court
OL,13,Fspoke to his character including one
OL,14,Fwhich described him as being "a good
OL,15,Fman with a good heart".
